reviews.text:
I had to buy almost everything and from different suppliers. I had to wait for about a month for everything to arrive and when they did I was a little bit lazy to mix it up because i had already 10 different freshly mixed new liquids. I decided to mix it though and actually SNV literally. "Oh-my-god!" This is simply amazing and probably my new addiction - goes straight to the top of best DIY recipes/liquids! Cigar (a very nice one), little bit of ash (seriously, just enough to remind of an actual smoke), little bit of fruit for sweetness and juiciness and the vanilla totally in the background blending all the flavours together. Totally worth buying the flavours required even if it is just for this (even though Shisha Vanilla and Mango are pretty awesome flavours anyway).&#xD;
&#xD;
Love you fear!
